## Dependencies

- **`/eval-harness`** — required for before+after baselines.
- **Frameworks (one of):** `axolotl-ai-cloud/axolotl`,
  `huggingface/trl`, `unsloth`, `huggingface/diffusers`, `nvidia/nemo`.
  Names as CHOICES, not mandates.
- **`huggingface-skills:hugging-face-model-trainer`** — optional
  orchestration on HF infra.
- **`huggingface-skills:hf-cli`** — for model download, upload, license
  probe.
- **Compute:** local CUDA, runpod, modal, lambda labs, HF endpoints.
  Skill emits the command; does not provision.
- **Cross-family:** `/recipe` (Family J) consumes RECIPE.md when
  formalizing a project as a reproducible paper supplement.

